name: NEKO NO YUMENOSHIMA - Everybody Has A Dream
description:
With all our different daily struggles in life, we all need a break sometimes to dream big. Inspired by a certain cat that struggles constantly and a place we all dreamed of visiting as kids. 

Let's not forget our dreams !

UNN0RM4L Artist: JaSha made, hand drawn design to digital Illustration.

UNN0RM4L.Studio collective of less fortunate or non crypto nerd artist that still produce distinctive and brilliant art pieces.

Because the basic knowledge of the #crypto #NFT world is missing, we aim to give them a chance to shine bright and be discovered in this beautiful modern world.

100% going to the artist or their families.
